<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Petition Midterm</title>
        <link href="/stylesheets/Petition.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
        <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
        <link
          href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
          crossorigin="anonymous"
        />
    </head>
      <body>
        <div class='container-fluid bg-light '>
            <img class="logo" src="/images/download.png" alt="">
            <div class="d-flex flex-row">
              <div>
                <div class="container bg-white border shadow-sm bg-white middle-box">
                  <h1 class="title">
                    Moving the 489 Lecture to the evening
                  </h1>
                  <div class="font">
                    Many people have signed this petition. Add your name now!
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-inline-flex profile-comments">
                    <img class= "profile" src="images/profile-icon-480x480-1.webp" alt="">
                    <div class="title-prof">
                      The Office of the Governor
                    </div>
                    <div class="title-comments">
                      161 comments
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container bg-white border shadow-sm p-3 bg-white middle-box">
                  <div class="d-inline-flex">
                    <img class="image" src="images/e8142d65ee88b33663deb97f95db7957.jpg" alt="">
                    <div>
                      <div class="text">
                        ***The Office of the Governor is the sponsor of this petition, but is NOT the group requesting donations of any kind. You are able to sign the petition without donating to ipetitions which is the platform hosting the petition. No donations to ipetitions is required. DO NOT DONATE.***
                      </div>
                      <div class="text2">
                        Our students deserve more than just a lecture. They deserve an evening
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="font1">
                    lecture
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    As a student and as your student, I want our class to have access to the best in educational services.
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    Limiting ourselves to having class in the morning ensures we will all be tired.
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    Expanding our vision to switch the lecture time to the evening SUPPORTS our classmates and faculty, DECREASES sleep that is lost, and IMPROVES the amount of sleep gained.
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    This lecture time switch will include:
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    <ul>
                      <li>Starting class at 5:00pm</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul>
                      <li>Many sleep schedules being fixed</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul>
                      <li>Happy Students</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul>
                      <li>A happy Professor</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul>
                      <li>A late end to the day</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul>
                      <li>Sweet dreams about Web development</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    Too many of our students have attended morning lectures. And for too long, we’ve accepted the status quo. We now have a unique opportunity to bring evening lectures here so that evening learning can start where it should–at WSU!
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    Join us on this mission to change the lecture time for 489!
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    For more information, click here.
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    Your Student,
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    David Navarro
                  </div>
                  <div class="body-text">
                    <div class="text3">
                      ***The Office of the Governor is the sponsor of this petition, but is NOT the group requesting donations of any kind. You are able to sign the petition without donating to ipetitions which is the platform hosting the petition. No donations to ipetitions is required. DO NOT DONATE.***
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container bg-white border shadow-sm bg-white middle-box">
                  <h5 class="comments">
                    Comment
                  </h5>
                  <table class="table table-hover">
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th scope="col">Name</th>
                        <th scope="col">Email</th>
                        <th scope="col">Comment</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      <% for (user of users) { %>
                      <tr>
                        <th scope="row"><%= user.nameuser %></th>
                        <td><%= user.email %></td>
                        <td><%= user.comment %></td>
                      </tr>
                      <% } %>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
              </div>
            <div class="container right-box border shadow-sm">
              <div class="container form">
                <h4>Sign this Petition</h4>
                <form method="post" action="/enter" onsubmit="return validateCredentials()">
                  <div id="liveAlertPlaceholder"></div>
                  <input type="text" id="nameuser" name="nameuser" placeholder="Name*">
                  <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email*">
                  <textarea class="form-control" id="comment" name="comment" rows="3" placeholder="Comments*"></textarea>
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-2">Submit</button>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <script
          src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
          integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
          crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
      </body>
</html>   